{"tid":1009020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"意大利反對歐盟支持委內瑞拉臨時政府","createTime":"2019-02-05T01:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T12:55:55.000Z","uid":64191,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ac2441498cd456e54422313f4f59a3ffec6b09d1","tid":1009020,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:44:51.000Z","msg":"Italy vetoed EU recognition of Venezuelan opposition leader Guaido &ndash; M5S source to RT<br />\n<br />\n成段新聞我只列重點<br />\n<br />\nRome has effectively derailed an EU statement meant to recognize Juan Guaido as Venezuela&rsquo;s interim leader if President Nicolas Maduro fails to set up snap elections, a Five Star Movement source confirmed to RT.<br />\n<br />\nItaly announced the veto at an informal meeting of EU foreign ministers that started on January 31 in Romania, the source said. <br />\n<br />\n而目前形勢，歐洲國家包括英、法、瑞典、西班牙、奧地利都支持臨時政府，歐盟亦要求馬杜羅重辦大選，但意大利今次唔跟隊，仲反對歐盟既聲明<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rt.com/news/450594-source-italy-regects-guaido/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rt.com%2Fnews%2F450594-source-italy-regects-guaido%2F&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=debc6bab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rt.com/news/450594-source-italy-regects-guaido/</a><br />\n<br />\n豬年黎到，當然要post下歐洲第一豬隊友既新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbbb699163492a7f1af21ad1878ec487d270bef1","tid":1009020,"uid":121146,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:48:35.000Z","msg":"做練邪惡軸心國諗法係唔同啲"},{"pid":"40e413c6d222bd42d8f0ed07daa730384ea82c8f","tid":1009020,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做慣邪惡軸心國諗法係唔同啲</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4bbdac6d01c53d7ed406de3a66222767f9b0c3fc","tid":1009020,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:50:10.00